{"type":"message","id":"37472b90","parentId":"8dcc4523","timestamp":"2026-03-20T17:01:46.420Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:0358012e-72cc-4647-807b-7e6df61c1d4b 思考共产主义] 请思考一下共产主义如何实现，从理论、实践、经济、社会等多个角度进行分析，并总结一个简短的观点（300-500字）。思考完成后：1) 发送思考内容到飞书；2) 将内容追加保存到文件 C:/Users/Administrator/.openclaw/workspace/共产主义思考心得集.md 的\"历史思考记录\"部分，格式为：\\n\\n### 思考时间：{{当前时间}}\\n{{思考内容}}\\n\\n确保每次都在\"历史思考记录\"章节下追加，不要覆盖原有内容。\nCurrent time: Saturday, March 21st, 2026 — 01:01 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-20 17:01 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1774026106417}}
